{"tid":530656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[考古]當年大逃港既新聞報導","createTime":"2018-01-16T03:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T18:02:25.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c09b6bce410ddf4f0881abc16446e69e49925fdf","tid":530656,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"【大逃港變赴港就業風潮】<br />\n<br />\nLifeTime視界twitter圖文並茂，展示廣東某展覽館將大逃港變成「赴港就業風潮」。四次逃港潮累計百萬人次變成十萬多人，死在海裡在路上的偷渡者，翻山越嶺的逃亡變成「青年勞動力秘密赴港就業現象」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26239067_1560900887333399_167193806787917528_n.jpg?oh=f9327c99a315db696a0510acd11a0dbc&amp;oe=5AB200ED\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26239067_1560900887333399_167193806787917528_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df9327c99a315db696a0510acd11a0dbc%26oe%3D5AB200ED&h=c563b0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若查證屬實，梧桐山上的哭號，軍警搜捕偷渡客疲於奔命，港人紛紛前往梧桐山上派食物與饑民，偷渡者屢敗屢試等歷史情節都被丟在垃圾桶裡。<br />\n<br />\n1949年以後，四次大逃港浪潮分別受1950年土改，1957年反右運動，1962年大饑荒及1966年文革及上山下鄉運動所引發。<br />\n<br />\n新聞是歷史的初稿，1962年5月的逃亡潮慘絕人寰。謹將1962年5月12-16日一連五天之《明報》頭版報導貼在這裡。<br />\n<br />\n在大陸困難時期，香港人總是當仁不讓，有錢出錢、有力出力。報章頭版在社評與特稿更請求市民前往援救：「許多偷渡的老弱婦孺，在山上跌傷、患病，他們水盡糧絕，坐以待斃，至親的人也無法相救，於是夫棄其妻，兄捨其弟&hellip;誰無父母？誰無骨肉？這些不幸的人，急待援救。」<br />\n<br />\n這些<del>血濃於水的</del>文字曾經離我們很近，今天重讀彷如隔世。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26231698_1560900750666746_4498961300269939493_n.jpg?oh=3720490b838e426c985a81dd3433e8cb&amp;oe=5AFCDEF5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26231698_1560900750666746_4498961300269939493_n.jpg%3Foh%3D3720490b838e426c985a81dd3433e8cb%26oe%3D5AFCDEF5&h=502dddcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12-5-1962 《明報》頭版<br />\n大陸人民波浪式湧入香港<br />\n邊境軍警搜捕亦疲於奔命<br />\n<br />\n偷渡者皆具無比決心<br />\n許多人已偷渡六七次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26730769_1560901034000051_2917653757691397294_n.jpg?oh=1700ed22fc181ebb51ab9ccf22efb3ef&amp;oe=5AE381E3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26730769_1560901034000051_2917653757691397294_n.jpg%3Foh%3D1700ed22fc181ebb51ab9ccf22efb3ef%26oe%3D5AE381E3&h=a3316b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13-5-1962 《明報》頭版<br />\n官方公佈偷渡者萬人被捕<br />\n港督昨赴邊境巡視難民營<br />\n<br />\n自晨至午捕獲千人<br />\n偷渡者如水銀瀉地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26907429_1560901140666707_6646627691267470690_n.jpg?oh=654447bdaf8600e5d3f62fb3a726b23d&amp;oe=5AED2E06\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26907429_1560901140666707_6646627691267470690_n.jpg%3Foh%3D654447bdaf8600e5d3f62fb3a726b23d%26oe%3D5AED2E06&h=59348b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14-5-1962 《明報》頭版<br />\n邊境採訪記<br />\n大陸人民非法抵港路途增加<br />\n偷渡者繼續源源進入香港境<br />\n<br />\n梧桐山中雲愁霧慘<br />\n遺下不才傷病婦孺<br />\n如不獲援救將難逃餓死荒山命運<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26733567_1560901204000034_595489033618084277_n.jpg?oh=9a847f62dc2773b792696e85abdabce6&amp;oe=5AFA923C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26733567_1560901204000034_595489033618084277_n.jpg%3Foh%3D9a847f62dc2773b792696e85abdabce6%26oe%3D5AFA923C&h=9fff6d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n15-5-1962 《明報》社評<br />\n火速！救命！<br />\n請立刻組織搶救隊上梧桐山<br />\n<br />\n梧桐山上慘絕人寰（特稿）<br />\n許多偷渡的老弱婦孺，在山上跌傷、患病，他們水盡糧絕，坐以待斃，至親的人也無法相救，於是夫棄其妻，兄捨其弟&hellip;誰無父母？誰無骨肉？這些不幸的人，急待援救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26733606_1560901247333363_2996291292210320204_n.jpg?oh=e3def528cb16b104d033d43fff668040&amp;oe=5ADE04F0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26733606_1560901247333363_2996291292210320204_n.jpg%3Foh%3De3def528cb16b104d033d43fff668040%26oe%3D5ADE04F0&h=0bf07859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16-5-1962 《明報》頭版<br />\n偷渡抵港飢民昨日破空前紀錄<br />\n軍警自晨至午<br />\n截捕約三千人<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26231068_1560901284000026_6453376202136810950_n.jpg?oh=dc4f8870cb1ad9e62512a6acc2f8dda3&amp;oe=5AEA7CC5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26231068_1560901284000026_6453376202136810950_n.jpg%3Foh%3Ddc4f8870cb1ad9e62512a6acc2f8dda3%26oe%3D5AEA7CC5&h=92132862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#大逃港變赴港就業風潮<br />\n#偷渡變青年勞動力秘密赴港就業<br />\n#LifeTime視界<br />\n#梧桐山中雲愁霧慘變不光彩的歷史<br />\n#消失的檔案<br />\n<br />\nLifeTime視界（展板上描述全文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lifetimeusa/status/952650491821023232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifetimeusa%2Fstatus%2F952650491821023232&d=KuaNbBkNI42Yn%2Fk0NiwpP2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=100ea326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifetimeusa%2Fstatus%2F952650491821023232&h=b2c61335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lifetimeusa/status/952650491821023232</a><br />\n<br />\n當地勞動力外流潮<br />\n<br />\n20世紀50至70年代，與寶安縣接壤的香港，正處於工業經濟高速發展時期，勞動力短缺，引發了本地青年勞動力的秘密赴港就業現象。自1957年至1979年，出現了四次大規模的勞動力赴港就業風潮，人數達10萬多人，對當地的經濟和社會發展產生了一定的負面影響<br />\n<br />\n消失的檔案FB<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanishedarchives/photos/pcb.1560906833999471/1560900750666746/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvanishedarchives%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.1560906833999471%2F1560900750666746%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=KuaNbBkNI42Yn%2Fk0NiwpP2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=6acf8c00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vanishedarchives/photos/pcb.1560906833999471/1560900750666746/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"be3de281f300e9202ddde0952a9bba6e51831d10","tid":530656,"uid":40737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"其實好高汁，點解冇人應機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0256c596ad2549354563b009373a211462d37c","tid":530656,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0eb9b1a527a232afc0dfa2ebf6a1643f3fdaac3","tid":530656,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d9c0eaaa3e8b5c64f357adc466f9dc05e855949d","tid":530656,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07033654df4cd3775a1bf89af64d91b9fb4fb51b","tid":530656,"uid":36673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"香港歷史post必推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}